divs: Sighting DetailsI WAS OUT ABOUT TOWN SHORTLY AFTER COMPLETING A JOB INTERVIEW.JUST TAKING PICTURES OF THE BEAUTIFUL SCENERY.IT WASN'T UNTILL I RETURNED HOME AND DOWNLOADED THE PICS WHEN I NOTICED AN OBJECT IN ONE OF THE PHOTOS,AND THEN ANOTHER.IM ALWAYS WATCHING THE SKYS FOR "UFO'S" AND I CAN TELL YOU IN COMPLETE HONESTY THAT THERE "WERE NO OBJECTS" IN MY FIELD OF VIEW (OTHER THAN THE SCENERY) WHEN I TOOK THE PHOTOS.NO BIRDS OR PLANES. PHOTO 153 SHOWS WHAT APPEARS TO BE AN WEDGE SHAPED OBJECT MOVING FROM THE RIGHT TO THE LEFT. PHOTO 156 SHOWS (?) IT MIGHT BE A BUG.VERY STRANGE.
